title: BRIEF-Suncor Energy sees FY 2018 total production between 740,000 Boe/D to 780,000 Boe/D
text:
May 1 (Reuters) - Suncor Energy Inc:
* SEES FY 2018 TOTAL PRODUCTION 740,000 BOE/D - 780,000 BOE/D
* SEES FY 2018 PRODUCTION FROM OIL SANDS OPERATIONS 425,000 BBLS/D- 455,000 BBLS/D
* SEES FULL YEAR 2018 TOTAL CAPITAL EXPENDITURES C$4,500 MILLION - C$5,000 MILLION
* SEES FY 2018 SUNCOR REFINERY THROUGHPUT 415,000 BBLS/D - 435,000 BBLS/D
* SEES FULL YEAR 2018 TOTAL SYNCRUDE PRODUCTION 150,000 BBLS/D - 165,000 BBLS/D Further company coverage:
